_task* is sent the checkpoint is updated. This gives positive feedback that the service call is successful.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I think it would be useful if the topic <em>/srcsim/finals/task</em> for a new task began right after the task was initiated and not after leaving the start box. The elapsed time could be held at zero until the start box is left. </p>\n<p>Any other time a <em>rosservice call /srcsim/finals/start_task</em> is sent the checkpoint is updated. This gives positive feedback that the service call is successful.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2017-05-01T02:15:30.751176+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2017-05-05T03:15:43.251574+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 151}